div.bibl: Svenska Kuriren, Mar. 5, 1914. [ANNUAL REPORT OF THE INDEPENDENT ORDER LADIES OF SVITHIOD]

body.p: The Independent Order Ladies of Svithiod has presented its report for 1913. There are twenty-three branches of the Order, and total assets amount to $40,874,61. The membership increased last year and is now 3,971. The Order paid out $10,050 in sick benefits last year, $1,975 for funeral help, and $272.75 was donated to the needy.
